# Cloud Build source upload exclusions.
# Only workers/, backend/, dev_ocr/ and infra/ are needed for builds.

.git
.claude/

# Large data files — never needed at build time.
# IMPORTANT : leading slash = ancré à la racine du repo. Sans le slash, `data/`
# matcherait aussi `frontend/src/components/Layouts/sidebar/data/` et autres.
/data/
/docs/

# Python artifacts
**/__pycache__
**/*.py[cod]
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/*.egg-info/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.venv/

# Terraform state / local overrides
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
*.tfvars

# Node / frontend — on garde frontend/ dans le contexte (Dockerfile s'y trouve)
# mais on exclut node_modules et build artefacts (refait dans le builder stage).
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/out/

# OS / editors
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
